Title : Malaspina Inlet
Text : '''Malaspina Inlet''' is an [[inlet]] on the east side of [[Desolation Sound]] in the [[British Columbia Coast|South Coast region]] of [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]], located between [[Malaspina Peninsula|Malaspina]] and [[Gifford Peninsula]]s.<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/4651.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Malaspina Inlet"]</ref>  Sidewaters include [[Thors Cove]] and, via it, [[Theodosia Inlet]], where the locality of [[Theodosia Arm]] is located.  The upper, southeastern, end of Malaspina Inlet near the [[Powell River, British Columbia|City of Powell River]] is called [[Okeover Inlet]].<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/45148.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Okeover Arm"]</ref> on the east side of which the steamer landing [[Larsons Landing]] is located.<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/38216.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Larsons Landing"]</ref>  [[Grace Harbour]] is located on north side of Malaspina Inlet on the southwest side of Gifford Peninsula.<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/11595.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Grace Harbour (harbour)"]</ref>

